OL,7,FA striking doctor will be called off
OL,8,Fthe picket line to treat sick babies
OL,9,Fand pregnant mothers in Nottingham,
OL,10,Fafter an agreement was reached with
OL,11,Fthe union.
OL,13,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,14,Fhas agreed an exemption with the two
OL,15,Fmain hospitals regarding the neonatal
OL,16,Fintensive care unit and obstetrics.
