OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FA five-day walkout by resident
OL,8,Fdoctors, formerly junior doctors, in
OL,9,FEngland began on Friday, with members
OL,10,Fof the BMA at picket lines across the
OL,11,Fcountry.
OL,13,FThe BMA has argued that real-terms pay
OL,14,Fhas fallen by around 20% since 2008,
OL,15,Fand is pushing for full "pay
OL,16,Frestoration".
