OL,7,FThe union took out national newspaper
OL,8,Fadverts on Friday, saying it wanted to
OL,9,F"make clear that while a newly
OL,10,Fqualified doctor's assistant is taking
OL,11,Fhome over #24 per hour, a newly
OL,12,Fqualified doctor with years of medical
OL,13,Fschool experience is on just #18.62
OL,14,Fper hour".
OL,16,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,17,Fcondemned the walkout, branding it
OL,18,F"reckless" and "irresponsible", and
OL,19,Fsaid the government would not allow
OL,20,Fthe BMA to "hold the country to
OL,21,Fransom".
