OL,7,FHe insisted the government is doing
OL,8,Feverything it can to minimise patient
OL,9,Fharm as thousands of doctors go on
OL,10,Fstrike over pay.
OL,12,FFollowing concerns over the safety and
OL,13,Fcare of very sick babies inat
OL,14,FNottingham City Hospital, an agreement
OL,15,Fhas been reached allowing a resident
OL,16,Fdoctor to leave the picket if they are
OL,17,Fcalled.
