OL,7,FIn a statement on social media, the
OL,8,FBMA said: "We have agreed a derogation
OL,9,Fat City Hospital, Nottingham for one
OL,10,Fresident doctor to support NICU on
OL,11,FSaturday and Sunday.
OL,13,F"If contacted we advise resident
OL,14,Fdoctors to return to work. Thank you
OL,15,Ffor your support for taking industrial
OL,16,Faction."
OL,18,FThey later added: "The BMA has agreed
OL,19,Fto a derogation for one resident
OL,20,Fdoctor at the Queen's Medical Centre,
OL,21,FNottingham.
