OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,F"This derogation has been agreed in
OL,8,Forder to support the obstetric
OL,9,Fdepartment this afternoon and evening
OL,10,F(Friday 25 July)."
OL,12,FITV News Central has approached
OL,13,FNottingham University Hospitals Trust
OL,14,Ffor a response.
OL,16,FThe trust is currently at the centre
OL,17,Fof the largest maternity inquiry in
OL,18,Fthe history of the NHS, with over
OL,19,F2,500 cases of neonatal deaths being
OL,20,Fexamined by senior midwife Donna
OL,21,FOckenden.
