OL,3,CStriking doctors can be called to
OL,4,Ctreat babies at maternity scandal
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FIt's also being investigated by
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Police for potential
OL,9,Foffences of corporate manslaughter,
OL,10,Ffollowing the deaths and serious
OL,11,Finjuries related to maternity care.
OL,13,FFollowing the announcement of a
OL,14,Fcriminal investigation, Nick Carver,
OL,15,FChair at NUH and Anthony May, Chief
OL,16,FExecutive, put out a joint statement.
OL,18,FIt said: "It is absolutely right that
OL,19,Fwe take organisational accountability
OL,20,Fwhere we have failed women, families
OL,21,Fand babies.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
