OL,3,CStriking doctors can be called to
OL,4,Ctreat babies at maternity scandal
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,F"We are deeply sorry for the pain and
OL,8,Fsuffering caused. We know that for
OL,9,Fmany families this harm and suffering
OL,10,Fwill be lifelong.
OL,12,F"Since joining the Board, we have
OL,13,Femphasised the importance of openness,
OL,14,Ftransparency and accountability in our
OL,15,Fleadership and decision-making. We
OL,16,Frecognise that there is more to do.
OL,18,F"We are fully committed to the ongoing
OL,19,Fpolice investigation and the
OL,20,FIndependent Review of Maternity
OL,21,FServices, led by Donna Ockenden.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
